## Attribution diagnostic added

Added scripts/audit-pentagon-trigger-attribution.mjs.

The script reads a trigger, matching ACK messages, and the bridge log, then
classifies the result as native-window success, bridge catch-up after native
window, late bridge/manual catch-up, or still pending. This prevents a late ACK
from being counted as native evidence when the trigger was unclaimed during the
native-only probe window.

Syntax check:

```
node --check scripts/audit-pentagon-trigger-attribution.mjs
exit: 0
```

## T5N late ACK attribution

Command:

```
node scripts/audit-pentagon-trigger-attribution.mjs --trigger-id 6fab7bd2-1b19-4cb6-8ecf-f9e65670a5a8 --hash T5N_CODEX_HARNESS_NATIVE_APP_PROBE_REFRESH_20260523 --native-window-seconds 30
```

